  2→ * These triple-slash directives defines dependencies to various declaration files that will be
  3→ * loaded when a user imports the Starlight integration in their Astro configuration file. These
  4→ * directives must be first at the top of the file and can only be preceded by this comment.
  5→ */
  6→/// <reference path="./locals.d.ts" />
